# 593a3660f4c046f89c9721a885c94e39
#: ../../howto/custom-model-fields.txt:467
msgid ""
"**Remember:** If your custom field needs the :meth:`.to_python` method to be"
" called when it is created, you should be using `The SubfieldBase "
