"For example, in the filter ``{{ var|foo:\"bar\" }}``, the filter ``foo`` "
"would be passed the variable ``var`` and the argument ``\"bar\"``."
msgstr "Par exemple, dans le filtre ``{{ var|foo:\"bar\" }}``, le filtre ``foo`` reçoit la variable ``var`` et le paramètre ``\"bar\"``."

# b3695931bb31485fb7819f4a0285bc5f
